snippet.title: Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak - Free Title Update 5: Amatsu & Risen Shagaru Magala
snippet.description:
The Looming Calamity, Amatsu, has set its gaze on Kamura Village.

Experience the thrilling climax to the Monster Hunter Rise story when Free Title Update 5 comes to Nintendo Switch and Steam on April 20!

But wait, this isn’t the end!? 

Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak is available now on Nintendo Switch and PC / Steam!
https://bit.ly/MHRiseSB

Start your journey today in Monster Hunter Rise, available now!
Nintendo Switch: https://bit.ly/MHRiseNSW
PC/Steam: https://bit.ly/MHRiseSteam
